author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Margaret Glaspy featuring previously unreleased footage, from when she visited The Current studio back in 2018.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 I Love You, Goodnight
00:04:08 Book With No Binding
00:06:17 Before We Were Together

Musicians
Margaret Glaspy — vocals, guitar
Julian Lage — guitar

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Producer – David Safar, Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
